    • Constructor Detail

      • GraphStage

        public GraphStage(Session s,
                  VotoMenuBar parent,
                  int id)
        Create a Graph stage that takes in the ID for the question to be loaded. Since this polls for an ID, this will not be a live graph. It will load from a previous question and be static.
        Parameters:
        s - - The session to pull the data from.
        parent - - The MenuBar that created the Graph
        id - - The ID of the questiondata to be loaded

      • GraphStage

        public GraphStage(Session s,
                  VotoMenuBar parent)
        Constructor that doesn't take in an ID. This will poll the current question from the given session and will update it every 1 second.
        Parameters:
        s - - The Session for which to poll from.
        parent - - The VotoMenuBar parent.
